<div id="main_content">
	<h2>Kevin Belfield, Ranganathan Kumar Named Pegasus Professors</h2>
	
	<p class="article_info">
		
			By UCF Staff
		
		<span class="date">April 6, 2011</span></p>
	
	
	
		<div class="article_img" style="width: 345px;">

			<img alt="Article Main Picture" src="../resources/sites/UCF/content/live/NEWS/2000/NE2504/en_US/pegprofsmain.jpg" height="226" width="345"  /> 
			
				<p class="photo_credit">Photo: Jason Greene</p>
			
			<p>Both were awarded the university's highest honor for faculty - the title of "Pegasus Professor."</p>
			
				<p class="note"><a class="full_photo" id="popup.jsp?article_id=00240041052a2b5bb012d44907649037f2">Full Photo</a></p>
			
			
			
			
					
						
						
						
					
			
			
			
					
						
						
							
								<h3>Story Images</h3>
								<ul id="story_images">
							
						<li>
						<a class="full_photo" id="popup.jsp?article_id=00240041052a2b5bb012d44907649037f2&amp;img_mode=2&amp;index=0">
							<img alt="Article Main Picture" src="../resources/sites/UCF/content/live/NEWS/2000/NE2504/en_US/belfield98.jpg"  />
						</a>
						</li>
						
						
					
			
					
						
						
							
						<li>
						<a class="full_photo" id="popup.jsp?article_id=00240041052a2b5bb012d44907649037f2&amp;img_mode=2&amp;index=1">
